      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Planning Node Types Task\n\nThis graph operates on the current planning nodeset as the baseline.\n\nThat baseline is already documented near the planning graph template and task-planning library surfaces. The work here is to reference that existing authority, tighten its semantics, and reconcile it with the broader planning library so future work speaks from one authoritative planning surface.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": true,
        "root": true,
