      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Constraint\n\nDefine the **Constraint** node type.\n\nQuestions to answer:\n- What counts as a hard constraint versus guidance?\n- Should constraints be typed (schema, UX, performance, policy)?\n- Can a constraint apply globally or only to a subgraph?\n- How should Codex treat constraints during implementation?\n\nOutput:\n- constraint categories\n- canonical fields\n- usage rules",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
