      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Open Question\n\nDefine the **Open Question** node type.\n\nQuestions to answer:\n- What distinguishes an open question from a risk or investigation?\n- Should it track owner, status, and resolution path?\n- Does resolution convert it into a decision, task, or note?\n- How prominently should unresolved questions appear in prompts?\n\nOutput:\n- lifecycle rules\n- canonical fields\n- resolution behavior",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
