      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Dependency\n\nDefine the **Dependency** node type.\n\nQuestions to answer:\n- Should dependency be a node type, an edge type, or both?\n- What extra meaning does a dependency node add?\n- Can dependencies represent external systems, prerequisites, or ordering?\n- How should blockers be modeled?\n\nOutput:\n- representation choice\n- canonical fields\n- connection rules",
        "memo": "",
