      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Acceptance Criteria\n\nDefine the **Acceptance Criteria** node type.\n\nQuestions to answer:\n- Should criteria be checklists, prose, or structured tests?\n- Are they attached to tasks, goals, or decisions?\n- How specific should they be for Codex execution?\n- Can they drive validation or auto-review later?\n\nOutput:\n- canonical format\n- attachment rules\n- verification intent",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
