      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Library Reconciliation\n\nThe existing `task-planning` library already documents the planning nodeset and its adjacent classes.\n\nCurrent practical task:\n- treat that documented planning nodeset as authoritative\n- align the broader library and task graphs to that baseline\n- keep `acceptance-criteria`, `risk`, and `dependency` visible as deferred or superset classes until they are explicitly promoted\n- avoid inventing duplicate planning node classes or duplicate documentation",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
